      3:  "Saturn in the 3rd house places discipline and sustained effort into the domain of communication, effort, and siblings. The 3rd is an Upachaya house — Saturn gains strength here with time. Writing or communication requiring sustained discipline over many years may produce genuinely significant results. The sadhana direction is engaging patiently with the long arc of Saturn's developmental demand.",
