      10: "Saturn in the 10th house, an Upachaya house, builds real and lasting authority through sustained disciplined engagement. Career tends to carry themes of authority, administration, or sustained public effort. What is built in career may come slowly but tends to last. The sadhana direction is ensuring the considerable authority Saturn eventually builds is used in genuine service.",
